Codendi is the Xerox solution for enterprise-wide software sharing and
reuse. Codendi has been patiently crafted by the Xerox Codendi Team and
has been constantly improved since January 2001 when the CodeX
initiative was launched internally at Xerox. Codendi offers an easy and
fully integrated access to the best in CVS, mailing lists, bug
tracking, message boards/forums, task management, site hosting,
permanent file archival, full backups, and total web-based
administration.

For more information on Codendi please visit our websites:
http://www.codendi.com


